ple in a coed dorm. Looking back, that was crazy.', 15748, 0), (478783, 'There''s only one true superpower amongst human beings, and that is being funny. People treat you differently if you can make them laugh.', 37865, 0), (478784, 'I have a memory like an elephant. I remember every elephant I''ve ever met.', 59745, 0), (478785, 'I saw a woman wearing a sweatshirt with Guess on it. I said, Thyroid problem?', 12194, 0), (478786, 'I used to sell furniture for a living. The trouble was, it was my own.', 64396, 0), (478787, 'Life goes by fast. Enjoy it. Calm down. It''s all funny. Next. Everyone gets so upset about the wrong things.', 17330, 0), (478788, 'I am not a member of any organized political party. I am a Democrat.', 1122, 0), (478789, 'I am certain there is too much certainty in the world.', 1532, 0), (478790, 'Everybody talks about the weather, but nobody does anything about it.', 48445, 0), (478791, 'The funny thing about having all this so-called success is that behind it is a certain horrible emptiness.', 9118, 0), (478792, 'I like long walks, especially when they are taken by people who annoy me.', 13077, 0), (478793, 'I''m quite sarcastic, and I''m funny, but not kind of funny. It''s a weird funny, and some people don''t get me, and some people do.', 69272, 0), (478794, 'I usually stalk fans because I think they''re really funny on Twitter. They don''t know it, but I''ll just go through their timelines, and if something is happening in the media, I always read fan accounts instead of the news because they have all the info and make the funniest jokes about it, so that''s how I get my gossip - by stalking fans.', 60670, 0), (478795, 'I call myself the Amusement Park. That''s because I''m funny and scary at the same time.', 25037, 0), (478796, 'I love mankind it''s people I can''t stand.', 151, 0), (478797, 'The parrot''s so funny. He imitates me and I don''t even realize he''s doing it. I''m walking around the house talking to myself and whistling and the